Title: Breath of Fresh Squidward
Plot: When Squidward finds out that SpongeBob and Patrick have been sneaking into his room every night to watch the sunrise, he installs an electrical fence to shield them away. But when he accidentally get zapped by his own fence, he turns into the happiest guy in town. Eventually, SpongeBob is tired of him when Squidward is stealing his job and his employee-of-the-month fame.
Writer: Nate Cash, Tuck Tucker, Richard Pursel
